ZH: 我有两只猫。
EN: I have two cats.

ZH: 他们有两个孩子。
EN: They have two children.

ZH: 这个箱子有两个把手。
EN: This box has two handles.

ZH: 我需要两颗药丸。
EN: I need two pills.

ZH: 这间房子有两扇窗户。
EN: This room has two windows.

ZH: 昨天我们去了两家餐馆。
EN: Yesterday we went to two restaurants.

ZH: 他们一起散步了两个小时。
EN: They walked together for two hours.

ZH: 我今年已经看了两次电影。
EN: I have already watched two movies this year.

ZH: 她有两个最好的朋友。
EN: She has two best friends.

ZH: 这件衣服只要两块钱。
EN: This clothing only costs two dollars.

ZH: 我和他们之间有两个小时的时差。
EN: There is a two-hour time difference between me and them.

ZH: 我要买两个香蕉。
EN: I want to buy two bananas.

ZH: 他们住在距离公园有两公里的地方。
EN: They live two kilometers away from the park.

ZH: 我要去两次超市。
EN: I need to go to the supermarket twice.

ZH: 这张桌子可以容纳两个人。
EN: This table can accommodate two people.

ZH: 我有两只手。
EN: I have two hands.

ZH: 他家有两辆车。
EN: His family has two cars.

ZH: 我有两条裤子。
EN: I have two pairs of pants.

ZH: 这个房间有两个灯。
EN: This room has two lamps.

ZH: 明天我们要坐两个小时的火车。
EN: Tomorrow we will take a two-hour train ride.
